---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import imageOne from "@assets/images/inONe.webp";
import imageTwo from "@assets/images/inTwo.webp";
---

<section class="px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-start">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <figure
        class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300"
      >
        <Image
          src={imageOne}
          alt="Persona disfrutando la vida en Colima"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-square md:aspect-[3/4] lg:aspect-square"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/30 to-transparent"
        >
        </div>
      </figure>

      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed md:text-lg md:leading-loose">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nunc at erat eu
        nunc feugiat auctor. Fusce congue justo ut magna placerat, nec volutpat
        mi sodales.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Columna derecha - Contenido principal -->
    <div class="space-y-6 lg:space-y-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-center">
        Gozamos del clima acogedor<br class="hidden md:block" /> en Cofrad√≠a
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse
          vel felis ut ligula pharetra dictum. Proin euismod, lorem nec feugiat
          malesuada, ligula dui tincidunt erat, id tempor eros elit vel arcu.
          Suspendisse vel felis ut ligula pharetra
        </p>

        <figure
          class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300"
        >
          <Image
            src={imageTwo}
            alt="Ambiente tropical de Colima"
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/20 to-transparent"
          >
          </div>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
